title: Service Jobs Now Require Bizarre Personality Test From AI Company
description: Paradox.ai, which is used by some of the biggest employers in the country, requires applicants to respond to dozens of confusing slides featuring a blue alien named Ash.

title: Broker That Sold Abortion Clinic Data Contracted with Air Force for ‘Targeting’
description: New documents show that SafeGraph, a company that previously sold location related to abortion clinics, was contracted to explicitly help the Air Force with “targeting” in “contested geographies.”
